Accounting & Finance Module
The most sensitive module. It requires Immutable Loggingâ€”you never update a transaction; you create a correcting entry.
@RestController
@RequestMapping("/api/finance")
public class AccountingController {
    
    @PostMapping("/ledger")
    @AuditLog(action = "POST_LEDGER_ENTRY") // Custom Annotation for compliance
    public ResponseEntity<TransactionResponse> postGeneralLedger(@RequestBody LedgerRequest request) {
        // Logic for double-entry bookkeeping
        return ResponseEntity.ok(financeService.processTransaction(request));
    }
}
